this is a whole bunch of simple refactorings

there are a few folders in here ordered by the level of code they apply to

in the first folder are refactoring tips at the syntaxish level; loops, conditionals, ...
one is at the function breakup level (ex. should this be more than one function?)
one is about where things are in your file (for readability, advaced for hoisting)
one is at the level of accross files 
...

this can cover more than one lecture